# Qadha-Salah Tracker

A simple and user-friendly app designed to help Muslims calculate and track their missed prayers (Qadha Salah).

## Features
- Calculate missed prayers based on years missed.
- Track completed prayers.
- Get reminders for pending prayers (coming soon).

## Why Use This App?
This app simplifies the process of tracking missed prayers by providing an organized and clear record.

## Future Plans
- Add notifications and reminders.
- Provide detailed analytics for user progress.
- Create a mobile-friendly interface.

## Contribute
We welcome contributions! Feel free to open issues or submit pull requests with improvements or suggestions.
